I"Õ<h1 id="freesk8-mobile-app">FreeSK8 Mobile App</h1>

<p>The FreeSK8 Mobile application is a cross platform solution to monitor and configure VESC based ESCs via Bluetooth &amp; provide a logging interface for the Robogotchi.</p>

<p>Available for Android &amp; iOS:
<br /><a href="https://freesk8.app" class="btn btn-primary fs-5 mb-4 mb-md-0 mr-2">Get FreeSK8 Mobile</a></p>

<h2 id="quick-start">Quick Start</h2>

<h3 id="scan-for-ble-devices">Scan for BLE Devices</h3>
<p><img src="https://codex.freesk8.org/assets/images/mobileapp/scan.png" alt="Scan for BLE Devices" /></p>

<h3 id="select--connect-to-supported-device">Select &amp; Connect to Supported Device</h3>
<p><img src="https://codex.freesk8.org/assets/images/mobileapp/scan.png" alt="Scan for BLE Devices" /></p>

<h3 id="supported-escs">Supported ESCs</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Robogotchi</li>
  <li>Xenigotchi</li>
  <li>Stormcore Integrated BLE</li>
  <li>Trampa NRF/BLE Module</li>
  <li>Xenith &amp; Unity ESC</li>
</ul>
